content.text:
The Legendary bow and a Swiftarrow: Legends speak of a powerful bow
and Swiftarrow hidden deep within a dungeon. The onion orion must 
complete dungeon's challenges, defeat enemies, 
and claim the legendary bow and Swiftarrow to shoot Swiftarrows.
